OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA breezier day compared to
OL,6,FMonday, with the best of any cloud
OL,7,Fbreaks and brighter spells in eastern
OL,8,Fareas. Staying rather cloudy with
OL,9,Foutbreaks of rain over western hills.
OL,10,FRain becoming more persistent and
OL,11,Fheavy by the evening. Relatively mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA band of rain, heavy at
OL,14,Ftimes, especially over western hills,
OL,15,Fwill quickly move eastwards across all
OL,16,Fparts during the evening, clearing by
OL,17,Fmidnight. Becoming drier with clearer
OL,18,Fspells. Windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
