OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA rather blustery day, with
OL,6,Fa mixture of sunny spells and showers.
OL,7,FThe showers are likely to be heavy at
OL,8,Ftimes, especially on western hills.
OL,9,FTemperatures near average.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FA
OL,12,Fband of rain, locally heavy, moves
OL,13,Ferratically southeastwards Thursday,
OL,14,Faccompanied by squally winds. Colder
OL,15,Fon Friday, with sunny spells and
OL,16,Fblustery showers. Drier, brighter and
OL,17,Fless windy on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
